{"lemma":"دُفْقاتٌ","slug":"دُفْقاتٌ","root":"د.ف.ق","root_slug":"د-ف-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ف-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12736","n12740","n12741"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8F%D9%81%D9%92%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12736","headword_ar":"دَفَقَهُ","root":"dfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, &c.) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Jm, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoqN","text_ar":"دَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) and by poetic license"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqN","text_ar":"دَفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He poured it forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he poured it forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out, with vehemence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) namely, water [&c.]. (S, Mgh, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufiqa AlmaA='u","text_ar":"دُفِقَ المَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water poured out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqa AlmaA='u","text_ar":"دَفَقَ المَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or this last, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoqN","text_ar":"دَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water poured forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out, with vehemence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but As disallowed its being used in an intrans. sense: (Msb:) [the forms of the verb commonly used intransitively are 7 and 5:] accord. to Lth, alone, (K,) i. e. in the 'Eyn, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqa AlmA='u","text_ar":"دَفَقَ الما=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~amoEu","text_ar":"الدَّمْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoqN","text_ar":"دَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufuwqN","text_ar":"دُفُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tears,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poured forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out, at once:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. TA:) but Az disallows this. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqa A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"دَفَقَ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruwHahu","text_ar":"رُوحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God poured forth his spirit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God caused him to die:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may he die."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) As says, I alighted at the abode of an Arab woman of the desert, and she said to a daughter of hers, Bring to him the drinking-bowl ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEus~","text_ar":"العُسّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): and she brought me a drinking-bowl in which was milk, and spilled it; whereupon she said to her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqato muhojatuki","text_ar":"دَفَقَتْ مُهْجَتُكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May thy blood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heart's blood, be poured forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as appears from a statement above, the right reading is probably"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufiqato","text_ar":"دُفِقَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muhojapN","text_ar":"مُهْجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  One says also, of a river, or rivulet, and of a valley,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqa","text_ar":"دَفَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [app. for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqa AlmaA='a","text_ar":"دَفَقَ المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became full so that the water poured forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overflowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it poured forth the water, from its sides."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqa Alkuwza","text_ar":"دَفَقَ الكُوزَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He poured forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scattered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the contents of the mug at once;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adfqhu","text_ar":"ادفقهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b5-  The verb is also used transitively and intransitively in relation to a beast: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqotu Ald~aAb~apa","text_ar":"دَفَقْتُ الدَّابَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made the beast to hasten,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go quickly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b6-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqati Ald~aAb~apu","text_ar":"دَفَقَتِ الدَّابَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beast hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went quickly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and [in like manner] one says of a quick camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY mi$oyihi","text_ar":"فِى مِشْيِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yatadaf~aqu","text_ar":"يَتَدَفَّقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastens, speeds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"presses forward, in his pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^utunu","text_ar":"الاُتُنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tadaf~aqati","text_ar":"تَدَفَّقَتِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wild she-asses hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went quickly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiqa","text_ar":"دَفِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqN","text_ar":"دَفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had his teeth standing outwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had his elbows far apart from his sides."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafiqa","text_ar":"رَفِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["Jm","K","S","Mgh","Msb","TA","JK"]},{"entry_id":"n12740","headword_ar":"دَفْقَةٌ","root":"dfq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of pouring forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in"},{"kind":"page_break","n":893},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at once,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1,) or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with vehemence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaqaAtN","text_ar":"دَفَقَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12741","headword_ar":"دُفْقَةٌ","root":"dfq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quantity poured forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at once,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufoEapN","text_ar":"دُفْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dfE","text_ar":"دفع"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,) [or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with vehemence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) of rain, [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a shower, fall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"storm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity that falls without intermission,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S and Msb and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dfE","text_ar":"دفع"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gush"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of blood, (Msb in that art.,) &c.: (S and Msb in that art.:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufaqN","text_ar":"دُفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufaqaAtN","text_ar":"دُفَقَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufuqaAtN","text_ar":"دُفُقَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufoqaAtN","text_ar":"دُفْقَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a Alqawomu dufoqapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ القَوْمُ دُفْقَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The party came at once,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, * TA, *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb"]}]}}